#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `-Djdk.tracePinnedThreads` system property **only works on Java 21-23**.\n"
"It has been removed in Java 24+. For Java 24+, use the JFR events or Quarkus testing extensions instead (see the xref:./virtual-threads.adoc#testing-virtual-thread-applications[Testing virtual thread applications] section)."
msgstr "系统属性 `-Djdk.tracePinnedThreads` *仅在 Java 21-23 版本中有效* 。该属性已在 Java 24 及更高版本中移除。对于 Java 24 及更高版本，请改用 JFR 事件或 Quarkus 测试扩展（参 xref:./virtual-threads.adoc#testing-virtual-thread-applications[见“测试虚拟线程应用程序”一节] ）。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `-Djdk.tracePinnedThreads` will detect pinned carrier threads while running tests on Java 21-23 (See xref:./virtual-threads.adoc#pinning[the virtual thread reference guide for details])."
msgstr "在 Java 21-23 上运行测试时， `-Djdk.tracePinnedThreads` 参数将检测被固定的承载线程（ xref:./virtual-threads.adoc#pinning[详情请] 参阅 xref:./virtual-threads.adoc#pinning[虚拟线程参考指南] ）。"

