#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This class models the HTTP interaction with the weather service.\n"
"Read more about the rest client in the dedicated xref:./rest-client.adoc[guide]."
msgstr "该类用于模拟与天气服务之间的 HTTP 交互。有关 REST 客户端的更多信息，请参阅专门的 xref:./rest-client.adoc[指南] 。"

