msgstr "请确保使用支持虚拟线程的 OpenJDK 和 JVM 版本，并使用 `./mvnw quarkus:dev` : 命令启动 _开发模式_ ："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Must be 19+, we recommend 21+"
msgstr "必须年满19岁，建议年满21岁"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Launch the dev mode"
msgstr "启动开发者模式"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Then, in a browser, open http://localhost:8080.\n"
"You should get something like:"
msgstr "然后，在浏览器中打开 http://localhost:8080 。您应该会看到类似以下的内容："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "As you can see, the endpoint runs on a virtual thread."
msgstr "如您所见，该端点在虚拟线程上运行。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "It's essential to understand what happened behind the scene:"
msgstr "了解幕后发生了什么至关重要："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus creates the virtual thread to invoke your endpoint (because of the `@RunOnVirtualThread` annotation)."
msgstr "Quarkus 会创建一个虚拟线程来调用您的端点（这是因为使用了 `@RunOnVirtualThread` 注解）。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When the code invokes the rest client, the virtual thread is blocked, BUT the carrier thread is not blocked (that's the virtual thread _magic touch_)."
msgstr "当代码调用 REST 客户端时，虚拟线程会被阻塞，但承载线程不会被阻塞（这就是虚拟线程 _的神奇之处_ ）。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Once the first invocation of the rest client completes, the virtual thread is rescheduled and continues its execution."
msgstr "一旦 REST 客户端的首次调用完成，虚拟线程就会被重新调度并继续执行。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The second rest client invocation happens, and the virtual thread is blocked again (but not the carrier thread)."
msgstr "第二次调用 Rest 客户端时，虚拟线程再次被阻塞（但承载线程并未被阻塞）。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Finally, when the second invocation of the rest client completes, the virtual thread is rescheduled and continues its execution."
msgstr "最后，当第二次调用 rest 客户端完成后，虚拟线程会被重新调度并继续执行。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The method returns the result. The virtual thread terminates."
msgstr "该方法返回结果。虚拟线程终止。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The result is captured by Quarkus and written in the HTTP response"
msgstr "Quarkus 会捕获该结果并将其写入 HTTP 响应中"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Verify pinning using tests"
msgstr "通过测试验证固定效果"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In the `pom.xml,` we added an `argLine` argument to the surefire and failsafe plugins:"
msgstr "在 `pom.xml 中，` 我们为 surefire 和 failsafe 插件添加了一个 `argLine` 参数："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `-Djdk.tracePinnedThreads` dumps the stack trace if a virtual thread cannot be _unmounted_ smoothly (meaning that it blocks the carrier thread).\n"
"That's what we call _pinning_ (more info in xref:./virtual-threads.adoc#pinning[the virtual thread reference guide])."
msgstr "如果虚拟线程无法顺利 _卸载_ （即阻塞了承载线程） `，-Djdk.tracePinnedThreads` 选项会输出堆栈跟踪信息。这就是我们所说的 _“锁定”_ （更多信息请参见 xref:./virtual-threads.adoc#pinning[虚拟线程参考指南] ）。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This flag **only works on Java 21-23** and has been removed in Java 24+. For Java 24+, use the Quarkus `junit-virtual-threads` extension described in xref:./virtual-threads.adoc#testing-virtual-thread-applications[the virtual thread reference guide], which uses JFR events to detect pinning across all Java versions."
msgstr "*此标志仅在 Java 21-23 版本中有效* ，并在 Java 24 及更高版本中已被移除。对于 Java 24 及更高版本，请使用 xref:./virtual-threads.adoc#testing-virtual-thread-applications[《虚拟线程参考指南》] 中所述的 Quarkus `junit-virtual-threads` 扩展，该扩展利用 JFR 事件在所有 Java 版本中检测固定操作。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Starting with Java 24, thanks to link:https://openjdk.org/jeps/491[JEP 491], `synchronized` blocks no longer cause pinning.\n"
"This means pinning is much less likely to occur on Java 24+, occurring only when native code calls back to Java code that performs blocking operations."
msgstr "从 Java 24 开始，得益于 link:https://openjdk.org/jeps/491[JEP 491] `，synchronized` 代码块不再导致“pinning”现象。这意味着在 Java 24 及更高版本中，“pinning”现象发生的概率大大降低，仅在本地代码回调执行阻塞操作的 Java 代码时才会发生。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We recommend enabling pinning detection in tests.\n"
"Thus, you can check that your application behaves correctly when using virtual threads.\n"
"Just check your log after having run the test.\n"
"If you see a stack trace (on Java 21-23) or pinning events (using the junit-virtual-threads extension), better check what's wrong.\n"
"If your code (or one of your dependencies) pins, it might be better to use regular worker threads instead."
msgstr "我们建议在测试中启用“固定”检测功能。这样，您就可以验证应用程序在使用虚拟线程时是否行为正常。只需在运行测试后查看日志即可。 如果您看到堆栈跟踪（在 Java 21-23 版本中）或固定事件（使用 junit-virtual-threads 扩展时），最好检查一下问题出在哪里。如果您的代码（或某个依赖项）发生了固定，最好改用常规的工作线程。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Create the `src/test/java/org/acme/TheBestPlaceToBeResourceTest.java` class with the following content:"
msgstr "创建 `src/test/java/org/acme/TheBestPlaceToBeResourceTest.java` 类，内容如下："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"It is a straightforward test, but at least it will detect if our application is pinning.\n"
"Run the test with either:"
msgstr "这是一个简单的测试，但至少可以检测出我们的应用程序是否存在“固定”现象。请使用以下任一方式运行该测试："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`r` in dev mode (using continuous testing)"
msgstr "`r` 在开发模式下（使用持续测试）"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`./mvnw test`"
msgstr "`./mvnw test`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"As you will see, it does not pin - no stack trace.\n"
"It is because the REST client is implemented in a virtual-thread-friendly way."
msgstr "正如您将看到的，它不会发生死锁——没有堆栈跟踪。这是因为该 REST 客户端是以支持虚拟线程的方式实现的。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/rest-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The same approach can be used with integration tests."
msgstr "集成测试也可以采用同样的方法。"

